data.description: Just in time for the holidays. Step into this resell home with a new home feel. Built only a year ago this beautiful home is ready to be rented. Front and backyard landscaping with a generous sized corner lot. Stepping inside you'll be greater with a spacious foyer leading into your living, dinning and kitchen. The gourmet kitchen and white cabinets are perfect for the chef in the family. The 3 panel glass sliding door allows you to bring the outdoors inside when opened allowing you to entertain any sized family. The 3 bedrooms and 2.5 restrooms including a powder room downstairs are spacious and inviting. You'll also have a Flex room/ Office just off the living room and a well sized loft upstairs. Check out this gorgeous home before it's gone.
